OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fwarm evening with plenty of sunshine,
OL,7,Fthen dry and mostly clear overnight. A
OL,8,Ffew isolated fog patches may develop
OL,9,Flater in the night. Staying rather
OL,10,Fwarm in urban areas, but locally much
OL,11,Fcooler in rural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAny fog rapidly clearing to
OL,14,Fleave blue skies and mostly unbroken
OL,15,Fstrong sunshine. Feeling warmer than
OL,16,Fon Saturday and increasingly hot by
OL,17,Fthe afternoon with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
