OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHot
OL,6,Fand sunny for the vast majority with
OL,7,Funcomfortably warm nights. Sea breezes
OL,8,Fmay bring a little relief to some
OL,9,Fcoastal regions at times. Temperatures
OL,10,Fwell above the seasonal average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
